{"tid":417948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被揭曾建議英國寫年報監察聯合聲明   譚惠珠現稱：最重要大家跟基本法","createTime":"2017-09-29T07:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T15:42:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b21e2eab4987f905a278b207e46e516a7feee7e9","tid":417948,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170929/s00001/f87303d3bf7c756dbc7df79dd861ba55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2Ff87303d3bf7c756dbc7df79dd861ba55.jpg&h=09563fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國政府每半年會就《中英聯合聲明》實施情况，向國會提交香港半年報告書。由本土研究社等組織發起的「香港前途研究計劃」，近期翻查英國政府解密文件，發現曾任港英行政局議員、現為港區全國人大代表的譚惠珠，曾經於1984年12月初、即聲明起草後兩個月，向時任英國首相戴卓爾夫人建議，就中英聯合聲明實施情况發表年報，令港人安心。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠今日出席鄉議局活動後回應事件時指，當時行政會與戴卓爾會面時「講咩同點講全部有分工」，指現時基本法比聯合聲明詳盡；被問到是否繼續需要英國監察，譚一再強調「最重要大家跟基本法，香港就冇事」。她指，英國相關聲明在外交上「一兩日就解決」，至於是否不再需要跟進報告，要由英國決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170929/s00001/1506661992861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2F1506661992861&d=hz2uHQdD25P5LPti95DZtNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=d50bbb76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2F1506661992861&h=3be2cc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170929/s00001/1506661992861</a>"},{"pid":"3ab13ce17863bfb507f14be0a937af4b257d1926","tid":417948,"uid":37232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"邊個係主人咪奶邊個鞋底"},{"pid":"b0a9b1a31bfbce89e0c4e71cd0e2ccc4589bd0d4","tid":417948,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_GR/grace127/PSN_PHOTO/804/f_8565804_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_GR%2Fgrace127%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F804%2Ff_8565804_1.jpg&h=6e89aafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869cdbe8da79c6d560c3011474fb40a2ac6350ef","tid":417948,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e327ed08c74f046e314bed0a339522bd1d78c87","tid":417948,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce255616ea3b06fe7caa99c599d1ddf088b7e80e","tid":417948,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abc933938f6de41b6fd909d26f5fd91e2599b99","tid":417948,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce304086294c843c9f197f58179b476962d66bc","tid":417948,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"漢奸, 英國人走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97558bfee329ed188c60e0b13f4d8753b94837d8","tid":417948,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b720d14dffe2d996bcaf0dff0ecc27b18f8565","tid":417948,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}